---
<header class="sticky top-0 z-10 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-stone-200">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-3 sm:py-0 sm:h-16 flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-2 sm:gap-0">
