    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <h3 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-stone-900 mb-5">Dr. Terje Eide</h3>
      <p class="text-lg text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-pretty">
        Terje is the founder of NeoResQ and the inventor of the UMP-123. He has practised
